    <texts>
      <txt a="X" c="X" e="-3" pt="1">Why is it important that you become familiar with the vessel, the equipment and your own duties on board as soon as possible?</txt>
      <txt crct="50" c="X">It is important for you to know so that you can find your way around without someone guiding you all the time.</txt>
      <txt crct="76" c="X">In an emergency situation you need to know what to do and the position and use of different safety and fire fighting equipment.</txt>
      <txt crct="18" c="X">In an emergency situation it is important  to know where to find the Safety Officer for reporting.</txt>
      <txt crct="15" c="X">It is important to know the port operational procedures for handling cargo.</txt>
    </texts>
